---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="社区 — 雕龙 DragonCraft" locale="zh">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>社区协作</h1>
    <p>叙事平权运动是共同的实践，不是单向输出</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-content">

    <!-- 知识星球入口 -->
    <div class="zsxq-banner">
      <div class="zsxq-banner-inner">
        <div class="zsxq-banner-text">
          <div class="zsxq-eyebrow">知识星球</div>
          <h2>雕龙叙事实验室</h2>
          <p>正在和朋友们讨论有趣的话题，一起来吧？</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://t.zsxq.com/CLU1d" target="_blank" class="zsxq-cta">加入星球 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid" style="margin-top: 40px;">
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">GitHub</span>
        <h3>开源协作</h3>
        <p>Fork仓库，提交案例，贡献Skill，参与国际社区讨论。</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill" target="_blank">访问 GitHub →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">案例</span>
        <h3>提交案例</h3>
        <p>分享你的真实叙事故事。案例将经过审核后在案例库展示。</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/issues/new?labels=case-study&template=case_study.yml" target="_blank">提交案例 →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Bug</span>
        <h3>报告问题</h3>
        <p>发现Skill或书籍内容的问题？提交Bug，我们会尽快修复。</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/issues/new?labels=bug&template=bug_report.yml" target="_blank">报告 Bug →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">功能</span>
        <h3>建议新功能</h3>
        <p>有新的场景Skill想法？想扩展某个现有Skill的功能？</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/issues/new?labels=enhancement&template=feature_request.yml" target="_blank">提出建议 →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">翻译</span>
        <h3>参与翻译</h3>
        <p>将Skill翻译为其他语言，让叙事方法论触达更多人。</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/discussions" target="_blank">参与翻译 →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">CI</span>
        <h3>自动合规扫描</h3>
        <p>每次PR自动触发禁用词检查，确保内容质量。</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/actions" target="_blank">查看 CI →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="section" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <h2 class="section-title">贡献规范</h2>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>✅ 欢迎</h3>
          <p>真实案例故事、新增场景Skill、优化现有Skill Prompt、翻译、文档修正</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>❌ 不接受</h3>
          <p>没有叙事要素的流水账、不真实的案例、不符合方法论框架的内容</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>⚖️ 版权</h3>
          <p>案例版权归属贡献者，详见 CLA 协议。商业使用前会联系你。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .card a { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--accent); margin-top: 10px; display: inline-block; }

  /* 知识星球 Banner */
  .zsxq-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px 36px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .zsxq-banner-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .zsxq-banner-text {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 200px;
  }
  .zsxq-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c9a96e;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .zsxq-banner-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .zsxq-banner-text p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .zsxq-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #c9a96e;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .zsxq-cta:hover {
    background: #e0c07a;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }
</style>
